movie.title: Parched 2: Hangry
movie.description_intro: A social media influencer brings her friends to an Airbnb lake house to party. When an appetite stimulant is mistakenly dumped into the lake and the guests go for a dip, they emerge ravenous and insatiable.

movies.title: The Final Wish
movies.summary: After the death of his father, Aaron returns home to help his grief-stricken mother and to confront his past. Going through his dad's belongings, he comes across a mysterious item that is more than it seems.

movies.title: Flight of the Living Dead
movies.summary: A scientist accidentally escapes containment aboard a plane during turbulence. After being gunned down by a guard, she reanimates - as a zombie. A U.S. air marshall, along with a police officer, a flight attendant and a handful of passengers who've survived, must ride out the flight just to stay alive.

movies.title: Wasteland
movies.summary: Wasteland is set in a world ravaged by a deadly virus and within that world is Scott Miller, a man who, against the odds, is trying to carve out some sort of life. The deadly infection that has ravaged the globe has almost totally wiped out the human race and Scott must spend his days finding water, food etc. Whilst trying to find uninfected people by radio, he must also avoid the many dangers that lurk in the outside world, while he waits for the return of the love of his life, Beth.

movies.title: The Alligator People
movies.summary: A newlywed couple sit in a train. The husband receives a frantic telegram. He gets off at a station to make a phone call, the train pulls away without him on it, and that's the last his wife sees of him. Years later after a long search she finally tracks him down on his family's southern estate where she discovers that a failed medical treatment has turned him into an alligator mutant.
